      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly mint condition \u2014 an outstanding example of a well-preserved used car that is exceptionally rare to find on the market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains its original luster, no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind, and all trim and moldings in perfect alignment. The interior is equally impressive, showing no signs of wear on the seats, carpets, dashboard, or headliner \u2014 it presents as though it has barely been used. All mechanical systems are in excellent working order, with smooth engine performance, responsive braking, and no known issues. This is a turn-key vehicle that requires no immediate investment \u2014 simply purchase and drive with full confidence. Priced fairly for its exceptional condition; serious buyers are encouraged to schedule an inspection.",
